TextEng: What in the hells are you doing here? Not that I don't mind the help, but I thought we were locked down tight.
Text: 뭐야, 여긴 왜 온 거요? 도움은 고맙지만, 완전히 봉쇄된 줄 알았는데.

TextEng: Patrol where you want and see where you get. Nothing but animals trapped in here. Stinking thieving peasant animals.
Text: 원하는 곳을 순찰해봐요. 여기엔 짐승들만 갇혀 있어요. 악취 나는 도둑 천민 짐승들.

TextEng: Damned if I know what settled them down, but I ain't seen any trouble for a while now.
Text: 뭐가 놈들을 조용하게 했는지는 모르겠지만, 한동안 말썽은 없었어요.

TextEng: This is the docks. Don't go blabbing it, but everyone knows that the docks are controlled by pretty shifty characters.
Text: 여기가 항구요. 떠들고 다니진 말고요, 근데 항구가 수상한 자들 손아귀에 있다는 건 다 알아요.

TextEng: With the chaos of the plague, everyone seems to be acting like animals. The streets are thick with thieves. Thick!
Text: 역병의 혼란 속에 다들 짐승처럼 굴어요. 거리에 도둑이 득실거려요. 득실!

TextEng: Just don't attract attention to us here. I don't want a mob killing me before the plague can, after all.
Text: 우리한테 이목을 끌지만 말아요. 역병 때문에 죽기 전에 폭도한테 죽고 싶진 않으니까.

TextEng: You want to play hero, fine with me, but as far as I'm concerned, the animals in this district can have each other.
Text: 영웅 놀이 하고 싶으면 그러시든지요. 내가 보기엔 이 지구의 짐승들끼리 서로 물어뜯게 놔두면 돼요.

TextEng: Careful in the Docks. There's lots of lowlife thugs. Should just barricade the lot of them.
Text: 항구에선 조심하시오. 쓰레기 건달들이 많아요. 걔들 다 가둬버려야 하는데.

TextEng: Whatever was getting the locals all worked up seems to be over, I guess. No trouble here at all besides the plague.
Text: 주민들 흥분하게 만든 게 뭐든 끝난 것 같아요. 역병 말곤 아무 탈 없어요.

TextEng: Citizen, identify yourself!
Text: 시민, 신원을 밝히시오!

TextEng: Wait. You a new recruit? Aribeth saddle you with this job? Well, good luck if you're supposed to patrol in here. You'll need it.
Text: 잠깐. 신병이오? 아리베스가 이 일 맡겼소? 여길 순찰해야 한다면 행운을 빌어요. 필요할 거요.

TextEng: What, you think a grunt like me might have found Aribeth's precious Waterdhavian things? That's what you are asking, isn't it?
Text: 뭐, 나 같은 졸병이 아리베스의 귀중한 워터딥 물건을 찾았을 것 같소? 그걸 묻는 거요, 그치?

TextEng: Bah! I got a briefing about those, all right, and then I was stuck here! Why tell me about them if I'm not gonna be looking?!
Text: 젠장! 그것들에 대해 보고는 받았어요. 그러곤 여기 처박혔지! 찾지도 않을 거면서 왜 알려준 거야?!

TextEng: The only thing I'll see while I'm standing here is more blasted thieves. Let 'em all rot, I says.
Text: 여기 서 있는 동안 볼 거라곤 빌어먹을 도둑들뿐이에요. 다 썩어라지, 내 말이요.

TextEng: What is there to know? The district is full of nothing but animals. The plague was all it took to let everything go to hell.
Text: 알 게 뭐가 있소? 지구엔 짐승들밖에 없어요. 역병 하나로 모든 게 개판이 됐소.

TextEng: Ah, that auction is a load of crap. I'd bet it's all just a plan to get people into the Seedy Tavern and mug them.
Text: 아, 그 경매는 다 헛소리요. 사람들 시디 선술집에 끌어들여서 털려는 수작일 거요.

TextEng: Of course I knew. The first thug we put down had a notice on him. It's just one more reason for these dogs to slaughter each other.
Text: 물론 알았죠. 우리가 처음 잡은 건달한테 공고가 있었어요. 이 개 같은 놈들이 서로 죽이는 이유가 하나 더 생긴 거요.

TextEng: And they won't stop at that, either! Did you know that one of these mongrels had the gall to think I would try to get Lord Nasher himself to come here?
Text: 거기서 멈추지도 않을 거요! 이 잡종놈 하나가 내가 나셰르 영주님을 여기로 모셔오려 할 거라고 생각할 배짱이 있었다는 거 알아요?

TextEng: As if I would waste my time. No, this lot can go to hell if they like. I'm just going to keep them from getting loose. Plague take them all!
Text: 내가 시간 낭비할 것 같소? 아니, 이놈들 지옥에 가고 싶으면 가라지. 난 그냥 빠져나가지 못하게 막을 뿐이오. 역병이 다 데려가버려라!

TextEng: Every animal in here has already proved themselves worthless in my eyes. You want to play babysitter to a pack of wolves, you go right ahead.
Text: 여기 있는 짐승들은 이미 다 가치 없다고 증명했어요. 늑대 무리 보모 노릇 하고 싶으면 얼마든지 하시오.
